            "language": "zh-CN",
            "id": "4496383"
        },
        {
            "title": "贝壳－W(02423)回购44.76万股",
            "description": "<div id=\"newsBody\">\n<span class=\"newsDetail\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family:MingLiu;Arial;\">&lt;汇港通讯&gt;    贝壳－W(02423)申报，於 New York Stock Exchange 5月14日回购44.76万股，每股作价6.61美元至6.76美元，涉资约300万美元。\n截至今日本财政年度回购的总股数为44.76万股。</span>\n</div>",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-16 09:41:53",
